1. List the customer names of invoice date 22nd march 2023.
mysql> select name from customer where id in(select cust_id from invoice_master where inv_date='2023-03-22');
+----------+
| name     |
+----------+
| arundati |
+----------+
1 row in set (0.00 sec)

