2. List the product name and price of each invoice item.
mysql> select pname,price from product where pid in(select pid from invoice_item);
+-------------+-------+
| pname       | price |
+-------------+-------+
| brush       |   192 |
| ice cream   |   306 |
| cookies     |   326 |
| cool drinks |   561 |
| pencil      |   714 |
+-------------+-------+
5 rows in set (0.00 sec)
*********************************************************************************************************************************************************


